standup.title: My high and my low
standup.summary: What was the highest and lowest point in the past day for you?
standup.description: Each person shares what the high and low was for them personally since you last met as a team. What was the thing that made them happiest or feel most excited? What was the thing that made them feel sad or frustrated?
benefits: See how your team is experiencing work
Open conversations about difficult things at work
